{"tid":1769093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美聯社: 629名巴基斯坦女孩作為新娘被賣給中國","createTime":"2019-12-04T14:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T05:52:26.000Z","uid":165683,"like":18,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"67a415c77a8e882182f7e4a3399b7b7546e876f8","tid":1769093,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"LAHORE, Pakistan (AP) &mdash; Page after page, the names stack up: 629 girls and women from across Pakistan who were sold as brides to Chinese men and taken to China. The list, obtained by The Associated Press, was compiled by Pakistani investigators determined to break up trafficking networks exploiting the country&rsquo;s poor and vulnerable.<br />\n<br />\nThe list gives the most concrete figure yet for the number of women caught up in the trafficking schemes since 2018.<br />\n<br />\nBut since the time it was put together in June, investigators&rsquo; aggressive drive against the networks has largely ground to a halt. Officials with knowledge of the investigations say that is because of pressure from government officials fearful of hurting Pakistan&rsquo;s lucrative ties to Beijing.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apnews.com/c586d0f73fe249718ec06f6867b0244e?fbclid=IwAR2_oThO0_8VqHhf0Ow9JbuBqj_bmiwjpIQaKAqctEYyHkw3EnCTWZu0t6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fc586d0f73fe249718ec06f6867b0244e%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2_oThO0_8VqHhf0Ow9JbuBqj_bmiwjpIQaKAqctEYyHkw3EnCTWZu0t6U&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=6de08e45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apnews.com/c586d0f73fe249718ec06f6867b0244e?fbclid=IwAR2_oThO0_8VqHhf0Ow9JbuBqj_bmiwjpIQaKAqctEYyHkw3EnCTWZu0t6U</a>"},{"pid":"68166a5867ca0279a379be68676cf3545701cd57","tid":1769093,"uid":310700,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif